1 Corinthians 2-3 And <f>ⓓ</f>I was with you <f>ⓔ</f>in weakness and in fear and much trembling,
1 Corinthians 2-4 and my speech and my message were not in plausible words of wisdom, but in demonstration of <f>ⓕ</f>the Spirit and of power,
