1 Corinthians 2-6 <pb/>Yet among <f>ⓗ</f>the mature we do impart wisdom, although it is not <f>ⓘ</f>a wisdom of this age or of the rulers of this age, <f>ⓙ</f>who are doomed to pass away.
1 Corinthians 2-7 But we impart a secret and hidden wisdom of God, <f>ⓚ</f>which God decreed before the ages for our glory.
1 Corinthians 2-8 None of <f>ⓛ</f>the rulers of this age understood this, for <f>ⓜ</f>if they had, they would not have crucified <f>ⓝ</f>the Lord of glory.
